Dark Pool Tracker — Alembic migration environment.

Common commands (run from the backend/ directory):

  Apply all pending migrations:
    alembic upgrade head

  Roll back one step:
    alembic downgrade -1

  Auto-generate a new migration after editing models.py:
    alembic revision --autogenerate -m "short description"

  Show current revision in the DB:
    alembic current

  Show full migration history:
    alembic history --verbose

  Emit SQL without touching the DB (useful for review):
    alembic upgrade head --sql
